org.jboss.jbossts.xts.recovery.coordinator.ba

Class SubordinateBACoordinatorRecoveryModule

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jboss.jbossts.xts.recovery.coordinator.ba.SubordinateBACoordinatorRecoveryModule
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    RecoveryModule, XTSRecoveryModule

    public class SubordinateBACoordinatorRecoveryModule
extends java.lang.Object
implements XTSRecoveryModule
    This class is a plug-in module for the recovery manager. It is responsible for recovering failed XTS BA subordinate (SubordinateCoordinator) transactions. (instances of com.arjuna.mwlabs.wscf.model.sagas.arjunacore.subordinate.SubordinateCoordinator) $Id$
